    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Class</p><p>Prerequisite: At least 8+ levels in Lunar Slayer</p><p>You bear the mark of a true Lunar Slayer, that being a warrior who discoveres powers and abilities beyond that of chakra, and beyond that of the Shinobi world.</p><p>You gain the following benefits; </p><p>You gain an additional weapon Trick Weapon Trick or an additional Caryll Rune.</p><p>(Pick one; This cannot be changed later).</p><p>You gain a Slayer Tool from another subclass you do not have levels in.</p><p>The tool gained uses the same attack bonus and Save DC as the tools of your primary subclass.</p><p>You regain half your uses of your Slayer's Tools on a short rest.</p><p></p>",
